OL,6,FHe thought the 'bouncing bomb' could
OL,7,Fbe used to attack moored battleships,
OL,8,Fbut research soon focused on using it
OL,9,Fagainst German dams and it played a
OL,10,Fmajor role in The Dambusters Raid in
OL,11,FMay 1943.
OL,13,FAndy Stowe, Associate director
OL,14,Fauctioneer and valuer at Auctioneum
OL,15,FLtd, said: "We're really lucky to see
OL,16,Fso many special items, but when you
OL,17,Fget something that special it gives
OL,18,Fyou goosebumps."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
