OL,6,FMr Stowe said the items had a
OL,7,F"staggering" amount of interest from
OL,8,Fpeople all over the world, including
OL,9,Fin America and Australia.
OL,11,F"They're a piece of world history, so
OL,12,FI understand the worldwide interest,"
OL,13,FMr Stowe said.
OL,15,F"Many of the RAF pilots that flew in
OL,16,Fthe Dambuster Raids weren't British in
OL,17,Forigin, so it had worldwide appeal.
OL,18,FAnd then after the Dambusters film was
OL,19,Fmade in 1955, there was even bigger
OL,20,Fappeal from people across the world,"
OL,21,Fhe explained.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
