OL,6,FThe mission, codenamed Operation
OL,7,F'Chastise', was one of the most
OL,8,Fdangerous air operations of the war,
OL,9,Fwith 53 men killed and three captured.
OL,11,FThe surving aircrew of 617 Sqaudron
OL,12,Fwere lauded as heroes, and the raid
OL,13,Fultimately gave a significant morale
OL,14,Fboost to the people of Britain.
